    <p>The gummy bear is the most iconic candy shape in the world — and until recently, every version required gelatin from animal collagen. That has changed. Pectin-based formulations have matured to the point where the best vegan gummy bears rival Haribo in taste and texture while eliminating animal-derived ingredients entirely. Whether you eat plant-based, have gelatin allergies, follow kosher or halal dietary requirements, or simply prefer cleaner ingredients, this guide identifies the 8 vegan gummy bears worth buying in 2026.</p>

