    </div>

    <p>This guide is part of our <a href="/candy/">vegan gummy candy</a> hub, which also covers <a href="/candy/organic-gummy-bears/">organic gummy bears</a>, <a href="/candy/vegan-gummy-worms/">vegan gummy worms</a>, and <a href="/candy/plant-based-gummy-candy/">plant-based gummy candy</a> across all shapes and types.</p>

