    <h3>Why SmartSweets Are the Best Vegan Gummy Bears Overall</h3>

    <p>SmartSweets dominates the vegan gummy bear market for one reason: they solved the sugar problem without sacrificing taste. At 3 grams of sugar per bag — compared to 34 grams in Haribo Gold-Bears — they represent a 91% sugar reduction while still delivering a genuine candy experience. The secret is allulose, a naturally occurring rare sugar that provides sweetness with minimal caloric impact, combined with stevia leaf extract for depth. The pectin-based gelling system creates a softer chew than gelatin but is satisfying in its own right.</p>

    <p>In our blind taste testing, SmartSweets ranked first in "repeat purchase intent" — the single most important metric for candy. Testers who tried them wanted to buy them again. The six flavors (raspberry, lemon, green apple, peach, pineapple, and orange) are individually recognizable, not the amorphous "fruit" flavor common in sugar-free candy. SmartSweets are available at Target, Whole Foods, Walmart, CVS, Amazon, and most major grocery chains — making them the easiest premium vegan gummy bear to find. For a broader look at the entire vegan candy category, see our <a href="/candy/">vegan gummy candy</a> hub.</p>

