    <p>YumEarth is the undisputed king of organic vegan gummy bears. Their formula prioritizes ingredient purity above all else: USDA Organic certification, real fruit juice concentrates for flavor, and colors derived entirely from real food sources — turmeric, carrot, purple sweet potato, and annatto. There are no synthetic dyes, no artificial flavors, and no controversial sweeteners. The trade-off is a higher sugar content (14g per bag from organic cane sugar), but for consumers who prioritize organic, clean-label candy over sugar reduction, YumEarth delivers more than any competitor at a fraction of the price. For more certified organic options, read our <a href="/candy/organic-gummy-bears/">organic gummy bears</a> guide.</p>

