    <p>If texture is your priority — if you want a vegan gummy bear that chews like a Haribo Gold-Bear — Lovely Candy Co is the answer. Their proprietary pectin blend achieves a firmness and elasticity that no other vegan gummy bear matches. Most pectin gummies are noticeably softer than gelatin; Lovely Candy Co has closed that gap by engineering a chew profile that gelatin loyalists will actually enjoy. The ingredient list is admirably short: cane sugar, tapioca syrup, pectin, citric acid, natural flavors, fruit and vegetable juice for color. The allergen-free formulation covers all 14 major allergens, making it one of the safest options for people with food sensitivities.</p>

